---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="M365 Full Stack Assessment - PowerReview Advisors">
  <!-- Load Chart.js for data visualizations -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
  
  <main>
    <!-- PowerReview Advisors Header -->
    <div class="advisor-header">
      <div class="header-content">
        <div class="brand">
          <h1>PowerReview Advisors</h1>
          <p class="tagline">Your trusted partner in understanding and securing your Microsoft 365 environment</p>
        </div>
        <p class="subtitle">We help you identify issues across your entire M365 stack, understand their impact, and create a clear pathway to success</p>
      </div>
      <div class="header-actions">
        <button class="btn primary" onclick="downloadExecutiveSummary()">
          <i class="fas fa-download"></i>
          Executive Summary
        </button>
        <button class="btn secondary" onclick="scheduleAdvisorySession()">
          <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
          Schedule Advisory Session
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Understanding Your Environment -->
    <section class="environment-overview">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i> Understanding Your M365 Full Stack</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">PowerReview Advisors has analyzed every layer of your Microsoft 365 environment to help you understand where you are today and where you need to be.</p>
      
      <div class="stack-visualization">
        <div class="stack-layer" data-score="62">
          <div class="layer-header">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
            <h3>Identity & Access Layer</h3>
            <span class="layer-score">62/100</span>
          </div>
          <div class="layer-content">
            <p><strong>What We Found:</strong> 847 users without MFA, legacy auth protocols active</p>
            <p><strong>Why It Matters:</strong> This is your front door - if compromised, attackers access everything</p>
            <p><strong>Business Impact:</strong> One compromised account can lead to full environment breach</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stack-layer" data-score="68">
          <div class="layer-header">
            <i class="fas fa-database"></i>
            <h3>Data & Information Layer</h3>
            <span class="layer-score">68/100</span>
          </div>
          <div class="layer-content">
            <p><strong>What We Found:</strong> No DLP policies, 156 sensitive files shared externally</p>
            <p><strong>Why It Matters:</strong> Your intellectual property and customer data are at risk</p>
            <p><strong>Business Impact:</strong> Data breaches lead to lost trust and regulatory fines</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stack-layer" data-score="71">
          <div class="layer-header">
            <i class="fas fa-desktop"></i>
            <h3>Apps & Services Layer</h3>
            <span class="layer-score">71/100</span>
          </div>
          <div class="layer-content">
            <p><strong>What We Found:</strong> Basic protection only on Exchange, Teams, SharePoint</p>
            <p><strong>Why It Matters:</strong> These are your collaboration tools - they need advanced protection</p>
            <p><strong>Business Impact:</strong> Malware in one app can spread to all connected services</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stack-layer" data-score="75">
          <div class="layer-header">
            <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
            <h3>Device & Endpoint Layer</h3>
            <span class="layer-score">75/100</span>
          </div>
          <div class="layer-content">
            <p><strong>What We Found:</strong> Inconsistent device compliance, no conditional access</p>
            <p><strong>Why It Matters:</strong> Unmanaged devices are entry points for attackers</p>
            <p><strong>Business Impact:</strong> Lost or stolen devices can expose your entire organization</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Understanding the Issues -->
    <section class="issues-explained">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-microscope"></i> Let's Break Down What We Found</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Our advisors help you understand not just what the issues are, but why they matter to your business.</p>
      
      <div class="issue-cards">
        <div class="issue-card">
          <div class="issue-icon critical">
            <i class="fas fa-user-lock"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>The MFA Gap Explained</h3>
          <div class="explanation">
            <h4>What's happening:</h4>
            <p>847 of your users can access M365 with just a password. That's like having 847 house keys under doormats.</p>
            
            <h4>Why it's critical:</h4>
            <p>Microsoft reports that 99.9% of compromised accounts didn't use MFA. Passwords alone aren't enough anymore.</p>
            
            <h4>Real-world impact:</h4>
            <p>One phished password = access to email, files, Teams, and customer data. It takes seconds to compromise, weeks to recover.</p>
            
            <h4>The good news:</h4>
            <p>MFA is one of the easiest and most effective controls to implement. We'll show you how.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="issue-card">
          <div class="issue-icon high">
            <i class="fas fa-folder-open"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>The Data Protection Gap</h3>
          <div class="explanation">
            <h4>What's happening:</h4>
            <p>Your sensitive data can leave your organization without any alerts or blocks. It's like having no security cameras at the exits.</p>
            
            <h4>Why it matters:</h4>
            <p>Whether it's accidental or malicious, data loss damages your reputation and triggers compliance violations.</p>
            
            <h4>Business perspective:</h4>
            <p>Your intellectual property, customer lists, and financial data are your competitive advantage. They need protection.</p>
            
            <h4>The solution:</h4>
            <p>DLP policies act as smart guards, watching for and preventing unauthorized data movement. We'll design them for your needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Your Pathway to Success -->
    <section class="success-pathway">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-road"></i> Your Pathway to Success</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">PowerReview Advisors doesn't just identify problems - we create a clear, practical roadmap tailored to your business needs and resources.</p>
      
      <div class="pathway-phases">
        <div class="pathway-phase immediate">
          <div class="phase-header">
            <div class="phase-icon">ðŸš¨</div>
            <div class="phase-title">
              <h3>Critical First Steps</h3>
              <span class="priority">Highest Priority</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="phase-content">
            <h4>Quick Wins - Maximum Impact</h4>
            <p>These are the most critical actions that provide immediate security improvements with minimal complexity.</p>
            
            <div class="action-items">
              <div class="action-item">
                <div class="action-header">
                  <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                  <span>Enable MFA for Administrators</span>
                </div>
                <div class="action-details">
                  <p><strong>Why first:</strong> Admin accounts are the keys to your kingdom</p>
                  <p><strong>How to do it:</strong> Azure AD > Security > MFA > Include all admin roles</p>
                  <p><strong>Complexity:</strong> Low - standard configuration</p>
                  <p><strong>Risk reduction:</strong> 90% for admin compromise</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="action-item">
                <div class="action-header">
                  <i class="fas fa-ban"></i>
                  <span>Block Legacy Authentication</span>
                </div>
                <div class="action-details">
                  <p><strong>Why important:</strong> Legacy protocols bypass all modern security</p>
                  <p><strong>How to do it:</strong> Conditional Access > New Policy > Block legacy auth</p>
                  <p><strong>Complexity:</strong> Low - policy configuration</p>
                  <p><strong>Risk reduction:</strong> Stops 70% of breach attempts</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pathway-phase short-term">
          <div class="phase-header">
            <div class="phase-icon">ðŸ“ˆ</div>
            <div class="phase-title">
              <h3>Foundation Building</h3>
              <span class="priority">Core Requirements</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="phase-content">
            <h4>Building Your Security Foundation</h4>
            <p>Essential security controls that form the foundation of a secure M365 environment.</p>
            
            <div class="initiatives">
              <div class="initiative">
                <h5>Identity Security Program</h5>
                <ul>
                  <li>Roll out MFA to all users (phased by department)</li>
                  <li>Implement Conditional Access based on risk</li>
                  <li>Deploy Privileged Identity Management</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="initiative-outcome">
                  <strong>Outcome:</strong> Secure identity foundation for all M365 services
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="initiative">
                <h5>Data Protection Framework</h5>
                <ul>
                  <li>Classify your sensitive data types</li>
                  <li>Create DLP policies for each classification</li>
                  <li>Train users on data handling</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="initiative-outcome">
                  <strong>Outcome:</strong> Automated data protection across all platforms
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pathway-phase long-term">
          <div class="phase-header">
            <div class="phase-icon">ðŸš€</div>
            <div class="phase-title">
              <h3>Advanced Protection</h3>
              <span class="priority">Maturity Goals</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="phase-content">
            <h4>Achieving Best-in-Class Security</h4>
            <p>Advanced capabilities that transform your M365 environment into a proactive, intelligent security platform.</p>
            
            <div class="advanced-items">
              <div class="advanced-item">
                <h5>Zero Trust Architecture</h5>
                <p>Never trust, always verify - across every layer of your stack</p>
              </div>
              <div class="advanced-item">
                <h5>AI-Powered Threat Detection</h5>
                <p>Microsoft Sentinel watching for threats 24/7 across all services</p>
              </div>
              <div class="advanced-item">
                <h5>Automated Response</h5>
                <p>When threats are detected, your environment responds automatically</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why This Approach Works -->
    <section class="approach-explanation">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Why This Approach Works</h2>
      <div class="approach-grid">
        <div class="approach-item">
          <div class="approach-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Gradual Implementation</h3>
          <p>We don't overwhelm your team or budget. Each phase builds on the previous, creating momentum and confidence.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="approach-item">
          <div class="approach-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-users-cog"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Business-Aligned</h3>
          <p>Security measures that make sense for your industry, size, and risk tolerance. No one-size-fits-all solutions.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="approach-item">
          <div class="approach-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Knowledge Transfer</h3>
          <p>We don't just implement - we teach. Your team learns to manage and maintain these security measures.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="approach-item">
          <div class="approach-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-check"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Proven Results</h3>
          <p>This methodology has helped dozens of organizations achieve 90%+ security scores while maintaining productivity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Expected Outcomes -->
    <section class="outcomes-section">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i> What Success Looks Like</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">When these recommendations are implemented, here's what you can expect:</p>
      
      <div class="outcome-categories">
        <div class="outcome-category">
          <div class="outcome-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Security Outcomes</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Dramatically reduced risk of account compromise</li>
            <li>Protection against 99.9% of password-based attacks</li>
            <li>Automated threat detection and response</li>
            <li>Complete visibility into security events</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="outcome-category">
          <div class="outcome-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Compliance Outcomes</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Meet regulatory requirements (GDPR, HIPAA, SOC 2)</li>
            <li>Demonstrate security controls to auditors</li>
            <li>Automated compliance reporting</li>
            <li>Data governance policies enforced</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="outcome-category">
          <div class="outcome-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Business Outcomes</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Increased customer trust and confidence</li>
            <li>Reduced operational disruptions</li>
            <li>Protected intellectual property</li>
            <li>Competitive advantage through security</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="implementation-note">
        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
        <p><strong>Implementation Note:</strong> The time and resources required will depend on your team's availability, technical expertise, and organizational complexity. PowerReview Advisors can help you assess these factors and create a realistic implementation plan.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How PowerReview Advisors Helps -->
    <section class="advisor-value">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i> How PowerReview Advisors Helps</h2>
      <div class="value-props">
        <div class="value-prop">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Deep Discovery</h3>
          <p>We use advanced tools and decades of experience to find issues others miss across your entire M365 stack.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="value-prop">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Clear Communication</h3>
          <p>We translate technical findings into business language, helping stakeholders understand the "why" behind each recommendation.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="value-prop">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-project-diagram"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Practical Roadmaps</h3>
          <p>Our pathways are realistic, budgeted, and designed to work with your team's capabilities and constraints.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="value-prop">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-life-ring"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Ongoing Support</h3>
          <p>We're not just consultants - we're advisors. We stay with you through implementation and beyond.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Next Steps CTA -->
    <section class="next-steps-section">
      <div class="next-steps-content">
        <h2>Ready to Secure Your M365 Environment?</h2>
        <p>Let PowerReview Advisors guide you from uncertainty to confidence. We'll help you understand your issues, create your pathway, and achieve security excellence.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <button class="btn primary large" onclick="scheduleAdvisorySession()">
            <i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i>
            Schedule Your Advisory Session
          </button>
          <button class="btn secondary large" onclick="downloadFullReport()">
            <i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i>
            Download Full Assessment Report
          </button>
        </div>
        <p class="cta-note">Our advisory sessions are collaborative workshops where we review your assessment together and start building your custom pathway to success.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    main {
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #f8fafc;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* Advisor Header */
    .advisor-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #334155 100%);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .brand h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      opacity: 0.8;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    .header-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn.primary {
      background: white;
      color: #1e293b;
    }

    .btn.primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    }

    .btn.secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: white;
      border: 2px solid white;
    }

    .btn.secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    /* Environment Overview */
    .environment-overview {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    }

    .environment-overview h2 {
      color: #1e293b;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .section-intro {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .stack-visualization {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .stack-layer {
      border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .stack-layer:hover {
      border-color: #3b82f6;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    }

    .layer-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .layer-header i {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: #3b82f6;
    }

    .layer-header h3 {
      flex: 1;
      margin: 0;
      color: #1e293b;
    }

    .layer-score {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #dc2626;
    }

    .layer-content p {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .layer-content p strong {
      color: #1e293b;
    }

    /* Issues Explained */
    .issues-explained {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .issues-explained h2 {
      color: #1e293b;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .issue-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(450px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .issue-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    }

    .issue-icon {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .issue-icon.critical {
      background: #fee2e2;
      color: #dc2626;
    }

    .issue-icon.high {
      background: #fef3c7;
      color: #f59e0b;
    }

    .issue-card h3 {
      color: #1e293b;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .explanation h4 {
      color: #334155;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .explanation p {
      color: #64748b;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    /* Success Pathway */
    .success-pathway {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    }

    .success-pathway h2 {
      color: #1e293b;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .pathway-phases {
      display: grid;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .pathway-phase {
      border-left: 4px solid;
      padding-left: 2rem;
    }

    .pathway-phase.immediate {
      border-color: #dc2626;
    }

    .pathway-phase.short-term {
      border-color: #f59e0b;
    }

    .pathway-phase.long-term {
      border-color: #10b981;
    }

    .phase-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .phase-icon {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .phase-title h3 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #1e293b;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .priority {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .phase-content h4 {
      color: #334155;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .phase-content p {
      color: #64748b;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .action-items {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .action-item {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .action-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1e293b;
    }

    .action-details p {
      margin: 0.25rem 0;
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }

    .initiatives,
    .advanced-items {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .initiative,
    .advanced-item {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .initiative h5,
    .advanced-item h5 {
      color: #1e293b;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }

    .initiative ul {
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      color: #64748b;
    }

    .initiative-outcome {
      padding-top: 1rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      color: #059669;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* Approach Explanation */
    .approach-explanation {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .approach-explanation h2 {
      color: #1e293b;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-size: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .approach-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .approach-item {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .approach-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin: 0 auto 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #2563eb);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .approach-item h3 {
      color: #1e293b;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .approach-item p {
      color: #64748b;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Outcomes Section */
    .outcomes-section {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    }

    .outcomes-section h2 {
      color: #1e293b;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

